"      Madrazo-De La Garza A, Dibildox M, Vargas A, et al, &ldquo;Efficacy and Safety of Oral Pantoprazole 20 mg Given Once Daily for Reflux Esophagitis in Children,&rdquo;",
"      <i>",
"       J Pediatr Gastroenterol Nutr",
"      </i>",
"      , 2003, 36(2):261-5.",
"      <span class=\"pubmed-id\">",
"       [PubMed",
"       <a href=\"UTD.htm?21/45/22231/abstract-text/ 12548064 /pubmed\" id=\" 12548064 \" target=\"_blank\">",
